285
00:25:03,119 --> 00:25:05,119
[SPEAKER_02] mogao o Francuzi uzimati.

286
00:25:05,119 --> 00:25:08,019
[SPEAKER_02] U našim medijima se nije moglo pročitati

287
00:25:08,019 --> 00:25:11,559
[SPEAKER_02] da je Traore, presednik,

288
00:25:11,559 --> 00:25:14,180
[SPEAKER_02] rekao Francuzima,

289
00:25:14,180 --> 00:25:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] amo, vanj.

290
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:21,200
[SPEAKER_02] veleposlanik njihoj skupio se ide iz ove srednjeafričke zemlje

291
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:26,160
[SPEAKER_02] i na zračno luci čeka zrakoplofrancuski da ga odveze.

292
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:31,460
[SPEAKER_02] Zvon je telefon Traore svojim osiguranju,

293
00:25:31,460 --> 00:25:33,039
[SPEAKER_02] amo, na zračnu luku.

294
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:40,940
[SPEAKER_02] kod veleposlanika, kod veleposlanika postrojeno 17 jesetovjetnih crnih kufera,

295
00:25:40,940 --> 00:25:41,880
[SPEAKER_02] diplomatski.

296
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:44,960
[SPEAKER_02] Diplomatska udara na pošta, znači ne može se otvarati.

297
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:50,619
[SPEAKER_02] On veleposlaniku, amo, otvorite to.

298
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:54,740
