299
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:56,960
[SPEAKER_02] on si tamo, otvori, otvori.

300
00:25:56,960 --> 00:26:00,519
[SPEAKER_02] Sada nabrajam šta je sve bilo, idemo redom,

301
00:26:00,519 --> 00:26:02,059
