302
00:26:02,059 --> 00:26:05,680
[SPEAKER_02] Drago kamenje, zlato,

303
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:11,359
[SPEAKER_02] zatim, ovaj, popis imena i načina

304
00:26:11,359 --> 00:26:13,720
[SPEAKER_02] na kako treba izvesti državni udar

305
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:18,579
[SPEAKER_02] i koje ljude dovesti na mjesto, mjesto Traore

306
00:26:18,579 --> 00:26:20,259
