307
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:22,460
[SPEAKER_02] i tako dalje i tako.

308
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:25,359
[SPEAKER_02] Sve, sve, sve bogatstva, ruda, rudnike,

309
00:26:25,359 --> 00:26:28,140
