313
00:26:36,579 --> 00:26:39,519
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, kolonijalni sustav pada, o čemu ja to govorim.

314
00:26:39,519 --> 00:26:41,539
[SPEAKER_02] I još takih primjer ima,

315
00:26:41,539 --> 00:26:44,259
[SPEAKER_02] ali to ne možete pročitati u ovim medijima,

316
00:26:44,259 --> 00:26:49,319
[SPEAKER_02] jer je narativ takav da oni hoće gurnuti u rat proti Rusije.

317
00:26:50,299 --> 00:26:53,720
[SPEAKER_02] Bogu hvala da sa druge strane, za sada,

318
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,180
