319
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:56,220
[SPEAKER_02] ili za nikoga,

320
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:59,180
[SPEAKER_02] ne sjede razumni ljudi i ne žele to.

321
00:26:59,180 --> 00:27:01,400
[SPEAKER_02] I svaki dan to naznačavaju.

322
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:03,539
[SPEAKER_02] Nemojte gurati u rat, mi nećemo i rat.

323
00:27:03,599 --> 00:27:08,900
