324
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:12,140
[SPEAKER_02] Jer imamo snage i sredstva da to riješimo vrlo brzo.

325
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:13,539
[SPEAKER_02] I to je njima rekao.

326
00:27:13,539 --> 00:27:18,220
[SPEAKER_02] I zato je ta izreka, Prašići, ali to nije Putin, on je rekao.

327
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:22,240
[SPEAKER_02] On je ponovio, to je prije nekoliko godina, koliko se mogu sjetiti, rekao, medvjede.

328
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:24,480
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, njegov orao glavni.

329
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:26,859
[SPEAKER_02] Na glavnom, da, on je trbuho zborac.

330
00:27:26,859 --> 00:27:27,920
[SPEAKER_02] Da, trbuho zborac.

331
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:30,200
[SPEAKER_02] E, recimo na takav način, ovo je ostalo.

332
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,759
[SPEAKER_02] I to je današnje stanje.

333
00:27:31,759 --> 00:27:37,880
