375
00:29:49,839 --> 00:29:51,000
[SPEAKER_02] Kao da se osjeća.

376
00:29:51,019 --> 00:29:53,799
[SPEAKER_02] Govorim koja je to opasno se tu krije,

377
00:29:53,799 --> 00:29:55,500
[SPEAKER_02] što sve se radi.

378
00:29:55,500 --> 00:29:57,940
[SPEAKER_02] Ta obezglavljenost.

379
00:29:57,940 --> 00:30:01,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ta narativ koji nema nikakvog smisla.

380
00:30:01,039 --> 00:30:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali gledajte, onda čujemo, sad ja to moram reći,

381
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno moram vas pitati,

382
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] ako se Rusima dozvoli to što žele,

383
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] evo njih kod nas.

384
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:12,539
[SPEAKER_02] Nemaju. Da, to je narativ bolji.

385
00:30:12,539 --> 00:30:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Nema potrebe Rusija.

386
00:30:13,559 --> 00:30:15,559
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto bi Rusija došla bilo gdje druga?

387
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:20,339
[SPEAKER_02] Ne radi se o tome, oni sve sprašavaju.

388
00:30:20,339 --> 00:30:22,619
[SPEAKER_02] Sad moramo dignuti na onu razinu,

389
00:30:22,619 --> 00:30:24,799
[SPEAKER_02] kaj je to boj, a to je duhovni boj.

390
00:30:24,799 --> 00:30:26,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ovdje je duhovni boj.

391
00:30:26,420 --> 00:30:29,799
[SPEAKER_02] Ako smo rekli da jedan narativ 500 godina biva,

392
00:30:29,799 --> 00:30:31,720
[SPEAKER_02] u kojem je,

393
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:34,599
[SPEAKER_02] u završnici svojom sa militantom,

394
00:30:34,599 --> 00:30:36,500
[SPEAKER_02] imate još ideologije.

395
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:39,220
[SPEAKER_02] Ideologije, ove četiri,

396
00:30:40,900 --> 00:30:43,299
[SPEAKER_02] fašizam, nacizam, komunizam

397
00:30:43,299 --> 00:30:46,519
[SPEAKER_02] i militant i liberalizam.

398
00:30:46,519 --> 00:30:50,200
[SPEAKER_02] Svi su oni izvorište ne u desnoj,

399
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,759
[SPEAKER_02] nego u lijevoj ideologiji.

400
00:30:51,759 --> 00:30:52,680
[SPEAKER_02] Ne su lijevi,

401
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:54,039
[SPEAKER_02] proizvod lijeve ideologije.

402
00:30:54,039 --> 00:30:56,980
[SPEAKER_02] Odnosno njihovi, oni su i sami po sve ideologije.

403
00:30:56,980 --> 00:31:00,440
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, lijeve misli, tako nazovemo.

404
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:03,099
[SPEAKER_02] Oni su, proizvod, svi oni, sva tako.

405
00:31:03,099 --> 00:31:06,140
[SPEAKER_02] E sad, gledat ćemo njihovo vrijeme trajanja.

406
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:08,539
[SPEAKER_02] Fašizam je bio neki 20 godina,

407
00:31:08,539 --> 00:31:10,160
[SPEAKER_02] nacizam, slično.

408
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:13,279
[SPEAKER_02] Komunizam je bio 80 godina.

409
00:31:13,279 --> 00:31:16,359
[SPEAKER_02] Ovaj militant i liberalizam je 30 godina.

410
00:31:16,359 --> 00:31:18,799
[SPEAKER_02] I kad ti sve njih skupiš,

411
00:31:18,799 --> 00:31:20,599
[SPEAKER_02] jer oni se pojavljivali jedna za drugim,

412
00:31:20,599 --> 00:31:21,500
[SPEAKER_02] znači, očigledo je,

413
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:23,140
[SPEAKER_02] neko vodio jednu te istu stvar,

414
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:24,460
[SPEAKER_02] samo mi je davao drugu boju.

415
00:31:24,460 --> 00:31:30,859
[SPEAKER_02] Nekih stotinja godina, ukupno.

416
00:31:30,859 --> 00:31:33,819
[SPEAKER_02] I sad, kad imate povijest ljudskog roda,

417
00:31:33,819 --> 00:31:35,900
[SPEAKER_02] i sad nešto što je 100 godina,

418
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:37,619
[SPEAKER_02] to je malo, malo područje,

419
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:40,579
[SPEAKER_02] ili ako ćemo uzeti ovih 500 godina,

420
00:31:40,579 --> 00:31:43,539
[SPEAKER_02] ovi 100 godina je završnica tih.

421
00:31:43,539 --> 00:31:47,099
[SPEAKER_02] I militant i liberalizam je doveo do kraja.

422
00:31:47,099 --> 00:31:49,359
[SPEAKER_02] Zato jer je on doveo do kraja,

423
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:50,819
[SPEAKER_02] ruše civilizaciju,

424
00:31:50,819 --> 00:31:51,819
