425
00:31:51,819 --> 00:31:53,980
[SPEAKER_02] a svaka civilizacija

426
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,819
[SPEAKER_02] je prije svega duhovna,

427
00:31:55,819 --> 00:31:57,819
