428
00:31:59,319 --> 00:32:01,900
[SPEAKER_02] I to je sada, tu Evropa došla.

429
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:04,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ovi ne mogu pristati, oni sve gube.

430
00:32:04,039 --> 00:32:07,180
[SPEAKER_02] Da oni pristane na mir,

431
00:32:07,180 --> 00:32:08,740
[SPEAKER_02] onaj sporazum koji je poni,

432
00:32:08,740 --> 00:32:10,660
[SPEAKER_02] a prihvatio ga Putin,

433
00:32:10,660 --> 00:32:11,960
[SPEAKER_02] koliko možemo vidjeti,

434
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,819
[SPEAKER_02] tu bi još bilo neke korekcije,

435
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:17,940
[SPEAKER_02] tada oni nemaju što što gube.

436
00:32:17,940 --> 00:32:20,220
[SPEAKER_02] Oni tada moraju izići vani.

437
00:32:20,220 --> 00:32:22,240
[SPEAKER_02] Moraju izići ta silna inflacija.

438
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:24,440
[SPEAKER_02] Moraju izići sve uništenje industrije

439
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:25,460
[SPEAKER_02] po Evropi što ima.

440
00:32:26,079 --> 00:32:27,640
[SPEAKER_02] A nemaju šćin opravdati

441
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:29,039
[SPEAKER_02] te svoje narative.

442
00:32:29,039 --> 00:32:32,539
[SPEAKER_02] I očigledno da je u Americi

443
00:32:32,539 --> 00:32:33,799
[SPEAKER_02] postoje dvi Amerike.

444
00:32:33,799 --> 00:32:36,640
[SPEAKER_02] Amerika, nazovit ćemo uvjetno

445
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,359
[SPEAKER_02] Trumpovska,

446
00:32:37,359 --> 00:32:39,680
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno suverenistička Amerika,

447
00:32:39,680 --> 00:32:42,019
[SPEAKER_02] što god mi misli o tome,

448
00:32:42,019 --> 00:32:43,619
[SPEAKER_02] i druga, ovaj,

449
00:32:43,619 --> 00:32:44,640
[SPEAKER_02] sotonska,

450
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:46,759
[SPEAKER_02] militantnog liberalizma.

451
00:32:46,759 --> 00:32:49,759
[SPEAKER_02] I Trump unutar Amerike

452
00:32:49,759 --> 00:32:50,740
[SPEAKER_02] ima ta dva,

453
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:53,039
[SPEAKER_02] raspolučenost Amerike.

454
00:32:53,039 --> 00:32:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da, on ima prilično problema doma.

455
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] sada se još ide baviti s ovim vanjskim...

456
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:59,140
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, mora, mora on s vanjskim.

457
00:32:59,140 --> 00:32:59,759
[SPEAKER_02] Ne može.

458
00:32:59,759 --> 00:33:02,019
[SPEAKER_02] Da moraš pokriti inflacija je velika,

459
00:33:02,019 --> 00:33:02,980
[SPEAKER_02] tiskanje para.

460
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:04,140
[SPEAKER_02] Nije njemu lako.

461
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,400
[SPEAKER_02] On se bori,

462
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,359
[SPEAKER_02] to se slače,

463
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:08,119
[SPEAKER_02] on se bori na dva bojišnice.

464
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:09,039
[SPEAKER_02] Barem dva, da.

465
00:33:09,039 --> 00:33:10,319
[SPEAKER_02] Barem, to je najmanje dva.

466
00:33:10,319 --> 00:33:11,579
[SPEAKER_02] I to prijeti.

467
00:33:11,579 --> 00:33:13,119
[SPEAKER_02] I sad je on,

468
00:33:13,119 --> 00:33:13,799
[SPEAKER_02] i sada,

469
00:33:13,799 --> 00:33:15,279
[SPEAKER_02] ko podržava taj,

